    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515330/extras/a62e889eeb1ebb53ab7368733811c121.avif?t=1729105856\" width=600 height=97 /></span>阿卡玛——无尽大海中的一座孤岛，出现了一种叫做“裂缝”的魔法现象。人类曾通过叫做“阿特扬”的魔法生物，从岛上获得无尽的能量。这种生物能实现魔法壮举，跟人类数世纪以来和谐相处，直到某件事毁了这种和谐。阿特扬消失了，成为了光粒，而岛几近荒芜，人类文明崩溃，自然重新占据了之前的繁荣城市和工业场域。在古代荣光的阴影下，几个世代过去了，直到裂缝开始吞噬这座岛，威胁残存人类的生存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monster Tribe让你化身为人类最后的希望，一位天生就能跟阿特扬沟通的智者，可以把他们从真实世界和裂缝之间的虚空唤醒。你要探索阿卡玛，收集众多阿特扬，训练他们，解开被遗忘已久的秘密。为什么阿卡玛陷落？什么导致阿特扬消失进入虚空？有办法阻止裂缝吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个人能扭转乾坤吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515330/extras/6f184af0743ec1485aa3e04098afe760.avif?t=1729105856\" width=600 height=97 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515330/extras/4e091bc3137384a4517a767ffa3fbf19.poster.avif?t=1729105856\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515330/extras/4e091bc3137384a4517a767ffa3fbf19.webm?t=1729105856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515330/extras/4e091bc3137384a4517a767ffa3fbf19.mp4?t=1729105856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>这座广袤岛屿有着悠久且恐怖的历史。阿特扬的消失毁灭了人类文明，只留下很少的幸存者，以及无数等待解开的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >唤醒阿特扬！他们活在真实世界和裂缝之间的虚空，成为了漂浮在岛上的光粒。运用你的天生连结力唤醒他们，再次利用他们的力量！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索古代遗迹和不详荒野。收集资源来升级装备，并帮助被唤醒的阿特扬成长。你需要这些。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭开前人遗失的知识和可怕的秘密。你能存活得足够久，来解开阿卡玛可怕的陷落之谜吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515330/extras/a768f67295e3477c5e534ea803188f87.avif?t=1729105856\" width=600 height=105 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515330/extras/de6009ddb58fc42e8aabf1d431ca0d38.poster.avif?t=1729105856\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515330/extras/de6009ddb58fc42e8aabf1d431ca0d38.webm?t=1729105856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515330/extras/de6009ddb58fc42e8aabf1d431ca0d38.mp4?t=1729105856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>自然重新占据了阿卡玛之前的繁荣城市，就不会轻易交出领地。阿特扬与人类和平共处数世纪后也不会轻易投降。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在回合制战斗中指挥怪物小队：战斗在网格上进行，最多可由四个阿特扬组成小队迎击敌人。思考、制定策略、击败敌人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >培养出一支强大到足以面对裂缝的队伍。随着你的阿特扬不断获取经验，使用PRG类角色系统管理他们的发展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >克服终极挑战，进入遍布于阿卡玛的古老之塔。面对凶残的怪兽，解决复杂谜题，解开这座岛的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 广袤岛屿待你探索，自然重新占据了这里曾经繁荣的人类文明。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 使用回合制系统在怪物小队间进行复杂的策略战斗——脑子比蛮力更重要！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 总共可收集、命令72个阿特扬，使用灵活的RPG系统把他们培养成强大的战士。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 利用岛上的特殊资源并抢救失落文明的遗迹，来解锁特殊变异形态。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 引人深思的故事：当人类为了生存孤注一掷时，有各种秘密等你解开，各种问题待你回答。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515330/extras/b87a1d8121e898f79bc189e6a038437e.poster.avif?t=1729105856\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515330/extras/b87a1d8121e898f79bc189e6a038437e.webm?t=1729105856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1515330/extras/b87a1d8121e898f79bc189e6a038437e.mp4?t=1729105856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
